egoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol';font-size:18px;font-weight:400;line-heigh=
t:29px;text-align:left;"><p style=3D"margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0"></p><p s=
tyle=3D"margin:10px 0">After 6 years of applying steady discipline Patreon =
Member Marcus Aureliuse and others around him just reached financial freedo=
m. No lottery tickets. Just consistent, grown-up rules. Now he=E2=80=99s cr=
uising on a retirement at a super young 40 on a roadtrip to Starbase for a =
SpaceX visit. Living proof the Rules work. =F0=9F=9A=80</p><h3>Top 3 Rule t=
akeaways:</h3><p style=3D"margin:10px 0"><strong>1. Slow down and keep lear=
ning like your future depends on it</strong> Markets scream at you daily. I=
gnore the noise. Stay insatiably curious. </p><p style=3D"margin:10px 0"><s=
trong>2. Less is more. Play smart, not often</strong> Think football, not s=
lot machines. Sometimes offense, sometimes defense =E2=80=94 but every move=
 calculated. He made most of his money from just <em>two</em> smart plays (=
SOL run =E2=86=92 TSLA at $150). The IA =E2=80=9C3 rocks in your pocket=E2=
=80=9D rule is gold: focus deeply on fewer things. <u>Overtrading is the fa=
stest way to give it back.</u></p><p style=3D"margin:10px 0"><strong>3. Bui=
ld your own conviction and stay resilient</strong> Never borrow someone els=
e=E2=80=99s belief =E2=80=94 know exactly why you own what you own. </p><p =
style=3D"margin:10px 0">h.t to Maximus </p><h1>His Note:</h1><blockquote><p=
 style=3D"margin:10px 0">"Hope it=E2=80=99s ok for me to share this here. <=
strong>@InvestAnswers</strong> has been a tremendous help along my investin=
g journey. A few tips I=E2=80=99ve learned over 6 years that has allowed me=
 and a few others to become financially free. Sorry if it=E2=80=99s long. <=
/p><ul><li><p style=3D"margin:10px 0">Slow down. Sometimes it feels like a =
race but markets are noisy. Daily content and opinions can be overbearing a=
t times!</p></li><li><p style=3D"margin:10px 0">Learn learn learn. Being in=
satiably curious is paramount to success. You have to level up with your we=
alth, otherwise you=E2=80=99ll end up losing it all. There=E2=80=99s a ton =
of books out there on Bitcoin. Read. Sign up for paid substacks. Education =
isn=E2=80=99t an expense, it=E2=80=99s an investment.</p></li><li><p style=
=3D"margin:10px 0">Markets can be like American football. Sometimes you pla=
y offense, sometimes defense, sometimes you throw a Hail Mary or kick a 3 p=
ointer. Though every decision should be calculated. Not Hail Marys every tr=
ade or perpetually play defense.</p></li><li><p style=3D"margin:10px 0">Res=
ilience. Mistakes happen. Looking past mistakes and moving on is key. Don=
=E2=80=99t give up no matter what. Brighter days will come.</p></li><li><p =
style=3D"margin:10px 0">Expect the unexpected. For me, my big win came from=
 Oct 2023 SOL run. Then rotating that into TSLA at $150. I=E2=80=99ve overt=
raded in the past, but the majority of my success came from two trades. Two=
!</p></li><li><p style=3D"margin:10px 0">Live a simple life. Learn to be ha=
ppy with less. There=E2=80=99s peace in that. Sometimes, more stuff =3D mor=
e headaches.</p></li><li><p style=3D"margin:10px 0">Plan plan plan. Can=E2=
=80=99t express how important this is. Plan for what-ifs so when they happe=
n, you know exactly what to do. Spreadsheets, apps, models. Just make sure =
you aren=E2=80=99t overanalyzing (analysis paralysis). It=E2=80=99s a real =
thing.</p></li><li><p style=3D"margin:10px 0">Never lean on someone for con=
viction. Leaning on someone else=E2=80=99s conviction is doomed to fail. Yo=
u have to know what you hold. When the bull begins to buck, conviction is y=
our saddle.</p></li><li><p style=3D"margin:10px 0">Less is more. I love Jam=
es analogy of 3 rocks in your pocket. Each rock is a trade. This makes you =
think more. Develop patience. Not easy.</p></li><li><p style=3D"margin:10px=
 0">Be nice. We are all human and make mistakes. The journey is just as fun=
 as the destination."</p></li></ul></blockquote><p style=3D"margin:10px 0">=
